    	<h4>Scoring</h4>
    		<dd>At the end of each round, when every player has layed down a card, the player whomst placed the highest card, of the initial suit played, will take the pile of cards played, and all points that come with it. On the first hand taken, the two middle floating cards, if any, will go to the losing hand.</dd>
