	    	<dd>The dealer can be choosen at random, and will deal every card until another round of cards can no longer be delt (these remaining cards are left in the middle pile)</dd>
	    <h4>Passing Cards</h4>
	    	<dd>Before the start of the round, all players must pass cards:</dd>
	    	<dd>Round 1 - all players must pass right.</dd>
	    	<dd>Round 2 - all players must pass left.</dd>
	    	<dd>Round 3 - all players must pass 2 to the right.</dd>
	    	<dd>Round 4 - all players must pass 2 to the left.</dd>
	    	<dd>Round 5 - all players MUST HOLD their hand.</dd>
	    	<dd>Round 6 - repeat from round 1 passing.</dd>
