	    	<dd>In order for the round to start, a player must start with the 2 of the suit of clubs. If no one is holding the 2 of clubs, it is in the middle pile, and thus the 3 of clubs will start the game. From there the game plays one player at a time clockwise until no cards are left.</dd>
